Povratak posle 15 godina: Partizan dobija pojačanje u stručnom štabu
01 Nov 2019, 11:29 by Nemanja
Fudbalski klub Partizan dobiće pojačanje u stručnom štabu u vidu bivšeg fudbalera Igora Duljaja, preneo je ,,Sportski žurnal“.
Posle 15 godina, Igor Duljaj će se vratiti u Partizan, gde će raditi kao pomoćnik Savu Miloševiću.
Duljaj je zanat ,,pekao“ u mlađim kategorijama Šahtjora iz Donjecka, a u međuvremenu dobio je i trenersku licencu.
On je za Partizan nastupao u periodu od 1997. do 2004. godine.

POVEZANE OBJAVE

Back after 15 years: Partizan gets reinforcements at headquarters
01 Nov 2019, 12:29 by Nemanja
Partizan football club will receive reinforcement at the headquarters in the form of former footballer Igor Dulaj, the Sport Journal reported.
After 15 years, Igor Duljaj will return to Partizan, where he will work as an assistant to Savo Milosevic.
Bake is a craft baker in the younger categories of Shakhtar from Donetsk, and in the meantime has obtained a coaching license.
He played for Partizan from 1997 to 2004.
